  "footnotes": [
    "The Thirteen Colonies (1607–1776) were British possessions along the Atlantic seaboard; independence declared July 4, 1776",
    "Louisiana Purchase (1803) from France doubled US territory; Mexican Cession (1848) added the Southwest",
    "Alaska was purchased from Russia in 1867; Hawaiʻi was annexed in 1898 after the overthrow of Queen Liliʻuokalani",
    "The Confederate States existed 1861–1865 during the Civil War; Reconstruction followed 1865–1877",
    "Alaska and Hawaiʻi became the 49th and 50th states in 1959"
  ]
